msgid "Layer styles are effects that are added on top of your layer. They are editable and can easily be toggled on and off. To add a layer style to a layer go to :menuselection:`Layer --> Layer Style`. You can also right-click a layer to access the layer styles."
msgstr ""

#: ../../reference_manual/layers_and_masks/layer_styles.rst:22
msgid "When you have the layer styles window up, make sure that the :guilabel:`Enable Effects` item is checked."
