#: ../../reference_manual/layers_and_masks/layer_styles.rst:24
msgid "There are a variety of effects and styles you can apply to a layer. When you add a style, your layer docker will show an extra \"Fx\" icon. This allows you to toggle the layer style effects on and off."
msgstr ""

